1
00:00:11,205 --> 00:00:13,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

2
00:00:15,472 --> 00:00:18,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nice to meet you. Thank you
for always looking after my brother.</font>

3
00:00:19,972 --> 00:00:20,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your brother?</font>

4
00:00:21,605 --> 00:00:24,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Uehara's older brother, Takuya.</font>

5
00:00:26,572 --> 00:00:28,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! You're Uehara's big brother?</font>

6
00:00:34,105 --> 00:00:35,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

7
00:00:36,072 --> 00:00:38,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Since Yuri was still asleep,</font>

8
00:00:38,305 --> 00:00:41,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think Uehara left already.</font>

9
00:00:41,472 --> 00:00:44,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry. It's my fault
for dropping in all of a sudden.</font>

10
00:00:44,605 --> 00:00:45,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK.</font>

11
00:00:46,505 --> 00:00:49,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've been busy with work
since Hisashi came to my place,</font>

12
00:00:49,105 --> 00:00:50,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so we haven't had a chance to talk.</font>

13
00:00:50,872 --> 00:00:54,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I was able to take a day off,
and decided to come for a visit.</font>

14
00:00:54,205 --> 00:00:55,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

15
00:00:56,972 --> 00:00:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I agree...</font>

16
00:00:59,072 --> 00:01:02,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that it's better to talk directly
with Yuri.</font>

17
00:01:05,405 --> 00:01:06,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here you go.</font>

18
00:01:06,805 --> 00:01:07,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

19
00:01:15,605 --> 00:01:16,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is good.</font>

20
00:01:17,705 --> 00:01:19,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I hate to admit it</i></font>

21
00:01:19,505 --> 00:01:21,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but he is really super handsome.</font>

22
00:01:22,505 --> 00:01:23,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">More than Uehara?</font>

23
00:01:23,839 --> 00:01:25,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep. They're like chalk and cheese.</font>

24
00:01:26,305 --> 00:01:28,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Chalk...</font>

25
00:01:28,605 --> 00:01:31,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah, Nao... is that right?</font>

26
00:01:32,705 --> 00:01:33,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

27
00:01:33,805 --> 00:01:36,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here. I hope that you like it.</font>

28
00:01:37,205 --> 00:01:40,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, thank you.
I appreciate your thoughtfulness.</font>

29
00:01:40,405 --> 00:01:43,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's my way of saying thank you
for always taking care of Hisashi.</font>

30
00:01:43,805 --> 00:01:47,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's quite fortunate to live with someone
as pretty as you.</font>

31
00:01:50,305 --> 00:01:52,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no, no... I'm not so...</font>

32
00:01:57,105 --> 00:01:59,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This situation is like...</font>

33
00:02:10,171 --> 00:02:11,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

34
00:02:11,705 --> 00:02:14,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please look after my younger brother.
Thank you for everything.</font>

35
00:02:16,405 --> 00:02:19,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you for everything as well.</font>

36
00:02:20,972 --> 00:02:22,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>What are you doing, Nao?</i></font>

37
00:02:25,839 --> 00:02:26,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisashi!</font>

38
00:02:28,772 --> 00:02:31,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yikes! Hisashi!</font>

39
00:02:31,205 --> 00:02:32,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's up with you? That's creepy.</font>

40
00:02:33,305 --> 00:02:35,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you went back to your home.</font>

41
00:02:35,705 --> 00:02:38,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I forgot my phone, so I came back for it.</font>

42
00:02:38,905 --> 00:02:41,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought I told you not to come here.</font>

43
00:02:41,105 --> 00:02:42,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But, Hisa!</font>

44
00:02:42,972 --> 00:02:44,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisa?</font>

45
00:02:44,205 --> 00:02:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'd like to see where you live and stuff.</font>

46
00:02:47,505 --> 00:02:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you have enough money?
Are you sure money isn't tight?</font>

47
00:02:50,405 --> 00:02:52,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so worried, I can't help it.</font>

48
00:02:52,872 --> 00:02:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not just your older brother,
but like your parent as well.</font>

49
00:02:56,205 --> 00:02:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come you told Yuri your address,
but didn't tell me?</font>

50
00:02:59,305 --> 00:03:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aw, shut up.</font>

51
00:03:01,839 --> 00:03:03,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is why I didn't want you to know.</font>

52
00:03:04,039 --> 00:03:06,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come on, I'm sure you're in a pinch,
aren't you?</font>

53
00:03:06,105 --> 00:03:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, just look how skinny you've--</font>

54
00:03:08,305 --> 00:03:09,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Quit touching me!</font>

55
00:03:09,905 --> 00:03:11,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know I don't gain weight easily.</font>

56
00:03:11,605 --> 00:03:14,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you eat properly, you'll grow more.</font>

57
00:03:15,572 --> 00:03:17,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Pipe down!</font>

58
00:03:18,505 --> 00:03:19,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri.</font>

59
00:03:19,905 --> 00:03:21,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">From what I've heard,</font>

60
00:03:21,505 --> 00:03:24,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it sounds like you couldn't care
less about me.</font>

61
00:03:25,105 --> 00:03:26,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aw, man. What a pain.</font>

62
00:03:27,305 --> 00:03:28,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you drinking, Yuri?</font>

63
00:03:28,905 --> 00:03:32,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Acting like you're Mr. Common Sense,
you traitor!</font>

64
00:03:32,105 --> 00:03:34,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now, like I told you several times before,</font>

65
00:03:34,205 --> 00:03:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I haven't betrayed you, Yuri.</font>

66
00:03:36,205 --> 00:03:37,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Just come back--
-Liar!</font>

67
00:03:37,939 --> 00:03:39,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You met your former girlfriend.</font>

68
00:03:39,572 --> 00:03:42,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-She's a work acquaintance.
-Work acquaintance?</font>

69
00:03:43,205 --> 00:03:45,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm in sales for a home builder.</font>

70
00:03:45,505 --> 00:03:48,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She is an employee for one of our clients.</font>

71
00:03:49,105 --> 00:03:51,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that's it? Yuri, if it's for work--</font>

72
00:03:51,905 --> 00:03:54,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You planned a vacation with her,
didn't you?</font>

73
00:03:54,872 --> 00:03:55,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

74
00:03:55,872 --> 00:03:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The two of you were cozily planning
a vacation abroad.</font>

75
00:03:59,505 --> 00:04:01,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's what you were planning, right?</font>

76
00:04:02,305 --> 00:04:03,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh...</font>

77
00:04:04,105 --> 00:04:05,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh...</font>

78
00:04:05,772 --> 00:04:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My friend just happened to see you
and sent it to me.</font>

79
00:04:09,972 --> 00:04:12,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, is that really Takuya?</font>

80
00:04:12,405 --> 00:04:15,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is... me...</font>

81
00:04:18,105 --> 00:04:20,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh? Hey!
-This thing...</font>

82
00:04:20,705 --> 00:04:22,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop and listen to me, would you!</font>

83
00:04:22,472 --> 00:04:24,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Where are you going?</font>

84
00:04:24,072 --> 00:04:26,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What are you going to do
with your wedding ring?</font>

85
00:04:26,572 --> 00:04:27,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Excuse me!</font>

86
00:04:28,505 --> 00:04:29,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm divorcing you! Divorce, you hear!</font>

87
00:04:29,939 --> 00:04:31,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yuri, wait!
-Let go of me!</font>

88
00:04:31,672 --> 00:04:33,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No! Don't! Don't!
-Darn you!</font>

89
00:04:33,305 --> 00:04:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will never forgive you!</font>

90
00:04:35,205 --> 00:04:36,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Ah!
-Ah!</font>

91
00:04:41,405 --> 00:04:42,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh my.</font>

92
00:05:06,405 --> 00:05:09,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, when Yuri calms down,
I'll tell her to return.</font>

93
00:05:10,405 --> 00:05:12,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Sorry for all the trouble.
-Just forget about it.</font>

94
00:05:13,105 --> 00:05:15,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When Yuri gets like that,
there's nothing that can be done.</font>

95
00:05:15,472 --> 00:05:16,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

96
00:05:17,005 --> 00:05:18,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's true, Hisa,</font>

97
00:05:18,805 --> 00:05:20,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but are you cooking for yourself?</font>

98
00:05:20,505 --> 00:05:23,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't tell me you're eating whatever,
like cup ramen or pizza?</font>

99
00:05:23,305 --> 00:05:24,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've always been like that.</font>

100
00:05:25,805 --> 00:05:26,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisa!</font>

101
00:05:27,405 --> 00:05:28,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Leave me alone.
<i>-Hey! Hisa!</i></font>

102
00:05:31,672 --> 00:05:35,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're brother really loves you,
doesn't he?</font>

103
00:05:35,672 --> 00:05:39,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's really annoying.
He's overly obsessive.</font>

104
00:05:39,205 --> 00:05:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aren't you going back home today?</font>

105
00:05:42,305 --> 00:05:44,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not when things are like this.</font>

106
00:05:44,405 --> 00:05:45,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll start staying here again.</font>

107
00:05:49,405 --> 00:05:50,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

108
00:05:54,505 --> 00:05:58,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder
if Takuya really did have an affair.</font>

109
00:05:58,972 --> 00:06:01,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't think he's that type.</font>

110
00:06:02,572 --> 00:06:04,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Divorce! Divorce!</font>

111
00:06:12,105 --> 00:06:14,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What a hopeless case.</font>

112
00:06:16,105 --> 00:06:17,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Does Takuya know?</font>

113
00:06:19,505 --> 00:06:22,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That you've always liked Yu--</font>

114
00:06:22,472 --> 00:06:23,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you dare tell him.</font>

115
00:06:24,705 --> 00:06:27,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-You saw how he acts toward me.</font>

116
00:06:29,972 --> 00:06:32,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If he ever found that out,</font>

117
00:06:32,705 --> 00:06:35,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sure he'd tell me to have her.</font>

118
00:06:39,972 --> 00:06:42,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But--
-He's always been like that.</font>

119
00:06:43,105 --> 00:06:45,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I said I wanted something...</font>

120
00:06:47,672 --> 00:06:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he'd always...</font>

121
00:06:50,572 --> 00:06:52,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">give a silly smile and let me have it.</font>

122
00:06:57,505 --> 00:07:00,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">At any rate, don't you dare tell him.</font>

123
00:07:03,405 --> 00:07:04,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Uehara's brother came over?</i></font>

124
00:07:04,972 --> 00:07:07,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Marina!
-Here! Ah.</font>

125
00:07:09,005 --> 00:07:10,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, what kind of guy is he?</font>

126
00:07:10,772 --> 00:07:14,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If he's Uehara's big brother,
he must be so totally high level!</font>

127
00:07:14,705 --> 00:07:17,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Cool type? Fresh faced?
He's going on my handsome list.</font>

128
00:07:17,605 --> 00:07:19,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Do I even exist to you?
-Huh?</font>

129
00:07:19,705 --> 00:07:23,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hmm, he's a nice guy,
but maybe a little flaky.</font>

130
00:07:23,472 --> 00:07:26,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">At any rate, he totally loves Uehara.</font>

131
00:07:26,305 --> 00:07:29,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But then he hardly seems to know himself.</font>

132
00:07:29,305 --> 00:07:31,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's kind of thickheaded.</font>

133
00:07:31,605 --> 00:07:34,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Which sounds like his brother is...</font>

134
00:07:35,805 --> 00:07:37,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">a male version of Nao?</font>

135
00:07:37,972 --> 00:07:41,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder what Uehara is really thinking
about this.</font>

136
00:07:41,205 --> 00:07:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

137
00:07:42,939 --> 00:07:46,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If things don't work out with Yuri
and his brother</font>

138
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:49,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder if he'll want her again.</font>

139
00:07:49,205 --> 00:07:51,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you still worried about that?</font>

140
00:07:51,105 --> 00:07:53,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, he's always liked her.</font>

141
00:07:53,305 --> 00:07:55,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He liked her in a special way.</font>

142
00:07:56,405 --> 00:07:59,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He said he's gotten over her.</font>

143
00:07:59,072 --> 00:08:01,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm not sure he really has.</font>

144
00:08:01,205 --> 00:08:03,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What about the other
of the top three boys?</font>

145
00:08:05,205 --> 00:08:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's totally truthful about his feelings
with you, right?</font>

146
00:08:08,205 --> 00:08:09,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

147
00:08:10,171 --> 00:08:13,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, could it be that you've become serious
about him since he said he likes you?</font>

148
00:08:13,972 --> 00:08:15,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, of course I haven't.</font>

149
00:08:16,205 --> 00:08:19,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just that being with him is getting
more awkward every day.</font>

150
00:08:19,772 --> 00:08:22,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's what we mean
by you're getting serious about him.</font>

151
00:08:22,705 --> 00:08:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

152
00:08:24,872 --> 00:08:27,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yoshikawa Nao.
-Here!</font>

153
00:08:29,939 --> 00:08:31,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">ENGLISH MINI TEST, 32 POINTS</font>

154
00:08:35,205 --> 00:08:36,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh oh.</font>

155
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:40,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Her troubled heart
has affected her scores.</font>

156
00:08:40,305 --> 00:08:43,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What was her score?
-32.</font>

157
00:08:43,472 --> 00:08:46,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-That's good for her.
-Mitsuishi!</font>

158
00:08:48,205 --> 00:08:49,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Nao.</i></font>

159
00:08:50,672 --> 00:08:52,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

160
00:08:53,705 --> 00:08:57,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What about practice?
-We're off this week.</font>

161
00:08:58,772 --> 00:09:00,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

162
00:09:02,805 --> 00:09:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uhm, you know.
-Uh...</font>

163
00:09:04,939 --> 00:09:07,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... Go ahead.</font>

164
00:09:09,705 --> 00:09:11,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri is still at your place, right?</font>

165
00:09:13,105 --> 00:09:14,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh.</font>

166
00:09:14,105 --> 00:09:17,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Actually, Uehara's brother came by.</font>

167
00:09:17,072 --> 00:09:19,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Seriously? So everything's been settled?</font>

168
00:09:19,605 --> 00:09:22,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">More like it added fuel to the fire.</font>

169
00:09:22,705 --> 00:09:24,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It just makes matters more complicated.</font>

170
00:09:24,905 --> 00:09:26,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know,</font>

171
00:09:26,405 --> 00:09:29,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">this is no time for you to be worrying
over another family's problems.</font>

172
00:09:29,705 --> 00:09:32,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Finals are coming up pretty soon.
Are you ready?</font>

173
00:09:32,839 --> 00:09:35,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, I'll be fine. Just fine.</font>

174
00:09:35,672 --> 00:09:36,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're so easy to read.</font>

175
00:09:39,105 --> 00:09:41,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're stuck with your studies,
just give me a call.</font>

176
00:09:42,305 --> 00:09:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you I'll be fine.</font>

177
00:09:46,205 --> 00:09:47,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you feel awkward?</font>

178
00:09:48,305 --> 00:09:49,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

179
00:09:49,972 --> 00:09:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When you're with me.</font>

180
00:09:54,605 --> 00:09:55,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, uh...</font>

181
00:09:57,072 --> 00:09:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess it's only natural.</font>

182
00:10:01,505 --> 00:10:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi... has your character changed?</font>

183
00:10:05,939 --> 00:10:06,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You think so?</font>

184
00:10:08,105 --> 00:10:09,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh.</font>

185
00:10:09,305 --> 00:10:11,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think you just didn't know
this side of me.</font>

186
00:10:12,205 --> 00:10:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

187
00:10:14,005 --> 00:10:18,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I said I'd wait for you,
but I didn't say I'd wait silently.</font>

188
00:10:19,405 --> 00:10:20,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bye.</font>

189
00:10:26,705 --> 00:10:29,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've told Nao that I like her.</font>

190
00:10:34,205 --> 00:10:35,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh.</font>

191
00:10:36,939 --> 00:10:37,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yo.</font>

192
00:11:01,605 --> 00:11:03,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Isn't that Takuya?</font>

193
00:11:04,805 --> 00:11:06,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder what he's doing?</font>

194
00:11:10,605 --> 00:11:11,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The ring!</font>

195
00:11:17,205 --> 00:11:18,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisa! Nao!</font>

196
00:11:19,105 --> 00:11:21,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to work.</font>

197
00:11:21,405 --> 00:11:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Wait a second!</font>

198
00:11:23,772 --> 00:11:25,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Hisa!</font>

199
00:11:33,105 --> 00:11:35,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see you didn't find the ring, did you?</font>

200
00:11:35,472 --> 00:11:38,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No, but I'll keep looking.
-OK.</font>

201
00:11:39,005 --> 00:11:41,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Come in here.
-Thank you.</font>

202
00:11:41,939 --> 00:11:44,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, but Uehara is at work.</font>

203
00:11:45,205 --> 00:11:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What am I apologizing for?</font>

204
00:11:47,505 --> 00:11:50,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK. I was just glad to see his face.</font>

205
00:11:52,105 --> 00:11:55,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really do love your brother,
don't you?</font>

206
00:11:55,872 --> 00:11:57,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well,</font>

207
00:11:57,105 --> 00:12:00,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it's always been just the two of us
for a long time.</font>

208
00:12:01,039 --> 00:12:05,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really are against
Uehara living alone, aren't you?</font>

209
00:12:06,305 --> 00:12:08,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, he's not exactly alone, though.</font>

210
00:12:10,505 --> 00:12:14,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's never been much trouble at all.</font>

211
00:12:14,605 --> 00:12:17,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He never showed much emotion,
and acted strangely mature.</font>

212
00:12:17,672 --> 00:12:20,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-A man-brat.
-Huh?</font>

213
00:12:20,405 --> 00:12:22,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri told me about that.</font>

214
00:12:24,572 --> 00:12:26,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, a man-brat.</font>

215
00:12:27,805 --> 00:12:31,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He always tolerates things
so he wouldn't cause me any worry.</font>

216
00:12:31,605 --> 00:12:33,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But--
-Oh, I know.</font>

217
00:12:34,405 --> 00:12:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He is sometimes childish.</font>

218
00:12:36,505 --> 00:12:38,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And he gets angry so easily.</font>

219
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:41,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, but that's what's
so cute about him.</font>

220
00:12:42,105 --> 00:12:45,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You think so?
-Yes, of course.</font>

221
00:12:45,305 --> 00:12:49,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's desperately trying to be mature,
but his emotions are showing all over.</font>

222
00:12:49,705 --> 00:12:53,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But he never says a word
when it comes to what's crucial.</font>

223
00:12:55,205 --> 00:13:00,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's why I've never thought of
forcing him to come back home.</font>

224
00:13:01,972 --> 00:13:03,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

225
00:13:03,205 --> 00:13:05,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's got his own reasons for doing things.</font>

226
00:13:08,972 --> 00:13:10,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I've always had a dream.</font>

227
00:13:10,839 --> 00:13:11,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A dream?</font>

228
00:13:12,705 --> 00:13:15,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm a little old to be thinking like this,</font>

229
00:13:15,672 --> 00:13:17,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but ever since I was a kid</font>

230
00:13:17,605 --> 00:13:21,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've always dreamed of living in a house
that I built.</font>

231
00:13:21,505 --> 00:13:24,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri would be there... and Hisa.</font>

232
00:13:26,205 --> 00:13:29,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I always thought it'd be nice
if we could live like that someday.</font>

233
00:13:30,605 --> 00:13:33,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I don't think
that "someday" will be arriving soon.</font>

234
00:13:34,472 --> 00:13:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Takuya...</font>

235
00:13:40,839 --> 00:13:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Takuya!</font>

236
00:13:42,605 --> 00:13:45,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want you to make up with Yuri.</font>

237
00:13:45,205 --> 00:13:46,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

238
00:13:46,305 --> 00:13:48,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, you can't let it go on like this.</font>

239
00:13:48,472 --> 00:13:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For Uehara as well,
if you two aren't happy,</font>

240
00:13:52,305 --> 00:13:53,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you'll never achieve that dream.</font>

241
00:13:56,305 --> 00:13:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Or did you actually have an affair?</font>

242
00:13:59,772 --> 00:14:01,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I didn't!</font>

243
00:14:01,205 --> 00:14:03,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like I told you yesterday,
we weren't planning a trip.</font>

244
00:14:03,805 --> 00:14:05,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was a business meeting.</font>

245
00:14:05,805 --> 00:14:07,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She wanted to clear up
the misunderstanding,</font>

246
00:14:07,505 --> 00:14:08,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so she went and called Yuri.</font>

247
00:14:08,839 --> 00:14:11,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then why haven't you explained that
to Yuri?</font>

248
00:14:11,205 --> 00:14:12,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I did.</font>

249
00:14:12,405 --> 00:14:14,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But she won't even listen to me.</font>

250
00:14:18,005 --> 00:14:19,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Takuya!
-Yes?</font>

251
00:14:20,572 --> 00:14:22,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got an idea. Trust me!</font>

252
00:14:26,105 --> 00:14:28,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here, here, here. Here you go!</font>

253
00:14:28,105 --> 00:14:30,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here's your special ramen!</font>

254
00:14:31,505 --> 00:14:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao... What's the meaning of this?</font>

255
00:14:35,705 --> 00:14:37,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you worry about it.</font>

256
00:14:37,572 --> 00:14:39,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This new ramen is on me.</font>

257
00:14:39,872 --> 00:14:41,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not what worries me.</font>

258
00:14:42,905 --> 00:14:45,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's <i>he doing here?</i></font>

259
00:14:45,205 --> 00:14:48,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know what they say about a man
and woman eating ramen together.</font>

260
00:14:48,205 --> 00:14:50,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-They can say what their really thinking.
-That's right.</font>

261
00:14:50,839 --> 00:14:53,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Our place is really popular with couples.</font>

262
00:14:53,572 --> 00:14:56,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even when things are all mixed up,
they get straightened out like ramen.</font>

263
00:14:56,605 --> 00:15:00,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I eat here every day,
but it hasn't helped a bit.</font>

264
00:15:00,305 --> 00:15:02,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's because you're eating alone.
No meaning in that.</font>

265
00:15:02,505 --> 00:15:03,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's so stupid.</font>

266
00:15:05,205 --> 00:15:07,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, this is delicious.
-This is great!</font>

267
00:15:12,805 --> 00:15:13,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Manager!</font>

268
00:15:23,772 --> 00:15:27,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, since we're here, I guess
I'll listen to what you have to say.</font>

269
00:15:28,005 --> 00:15:31,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, that'd be perfect for Hisa!</font>

270
00:15:31,605 --> 00:15:32,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-When is this?</font>

271
00:15:33,005 --> 00:15:34,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The beginning of next week.</font>

272
00:15:34,772 --> 00:15:37,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Ramen eating competition.
Champion eats for free."</font>

273
00:15:37,205 --> 00:15:39,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisa would win for sure,
don't you agree, Yuri...</font>

274
00:15:40,205 --> 00:15:41,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

275
00:15:45,939 --> 00:15:49,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Damn him.
He's so obsessed with his brother.</font>

276
00:15:49,505 --> 00:15:50,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri!</font>

277
00:15:53,472 --> 00:15:54,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, Yuri--</font>

278
00:15:54,772 --> 00:15:56,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry about that.</font>

279
00:15:57,572 --> 00:15:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've caused you trouble now too, Nao.</font>

280
00:16:00,705 --> 00:16:03,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-That doesn't bother me.
-Nao,</font>

281
00:16:03,672 --> 00:16:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know you told me
it's OK to be a fool if you like someone.</font>

282
00:16:09,939 --> 00:16:11,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But...</font>

283
00:16:12,905 --> 00:16:15,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that's not exactly easy either.</font>

284
00:16:17,405 --> 00:16:19,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe I'll have an affair too.</font>

285
00:16:21,305 --> 00:16:23,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Yeah, that's what I'll do.</font>

286
00:16:24,039 --> 00:16:26,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, I've got lots of guy friends.</font>

287
00:16:27,839 --> 00:16:31,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">First I'll contact Onishi.</font>

288
00:16:31,305 --> 00:16:32,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! Don't do that!</font>

289
00:16:38,772 --> 00:16:40,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can't do that.</font>

290
00:16:41,872 --> 00:16:43,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Having an affair...</font>

291
00:16:45,972 --> 00:16:47,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's just plain cruel.</font>

292
00:16:50,905 --> 00:16:53,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Naturally it would be so to Takuya.</font>

293
00:16:53,305 --> 00:16:55,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And to this Onishi as well.</font>

294
00:16:58,872 --> 00:17:02,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And to... Uehara...</font>

295
00:17:09,072 --> 00:17:10,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara...</font>

296
00:17:11,805 --> 00:17:14,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">has always liked you, Yuri.</font>

297
00:17:17,605 --> 00:17:20,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But he removed himself from the picture...</font>

298
00:17:22,805 --> 00:17:24,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so you two could be happy.</font>

299
00:17:27,005 --> 00:17:28,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So how can you...</font>

300
00:17:29,405 --> 00:17:34,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">how can you say you'll get divorced...
or have an affair so easily?</font>

301
00:17:37,105 --> 00:17:38,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That kind of thing...</font>

302
00:17:40,972 --> 00:17:43,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">would be super cruel to Uehara!</font>

303
00:17:56,672 --> 00:17:58,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

304
00:18:05,805 --> 00:18:07,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">ISSEI</font>

305
00:18:09,305 --> 00:18:11,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Go back.
-Huh?</font>

306
00:18:12,705 --> 00:18:14,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't be having any affair.</font>

307
00:18:17,705 --> 00:18:19,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But--
-Don't you worry.</font>

308
00:18:21,405 --> 00:18:22,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK?</font>

309
00:18:51,972 --> 00:18:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you... Nao.</font>

310
00:18:57,905 --> 00:19:00,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">COFFEE SHOP</font>

311
00:19:07,305 --> 00:19:09,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've told Nao that I like her.</font>

312
00:19:26,072 --> 00:19:29,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara's as sullen as ever again today.</font>

313
00:19:29,605 --> 00:19:32,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I wonder if it's about that?
-What?</font>

314
00:19:33,039 --> 00:19:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That guy from my class
who came here the other day.</font>

315
00:19:36,205 --> 00:19:38,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He and I were getting along really well.</font>

316
00:19:38,772 --> 00:19:39,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, so?</font>

317
00:19:39,839 --> 00:19:42,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No matter how handsome a guy is,
when he thinks about the girl he likes,</font>

318
00:19:43,039 --> 00:19:45,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you can tell he's in love when he's
happy and anxious at the same time.</font>

319
00:19:45,939 --> 00:19:47,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

320
00:19:51,605 --> 00:19:52,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey.</font>

321
00:19:54,305 --> 00:19:55,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey.</font>

322
00:20:03,705 --> 00:20:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dad,</font>

323
00:20:05,305 --> 00:20:08,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">how will I get him to forgive me?</font>

324
00:20:08,505 --> 00:20:10,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hold on here. Where's today's horoscope?</font>

325
00:20:10,939 --> 00:20:14,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, let's see. It says to face north.</font>

326
00:20:14,905 --> 00:20:16,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Which is north?</font>

327
00:20:16,405 --> 00:20:18,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Yes?</i></font>

328
00:20:19,005 --> 00:20:20,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh.
-Daichi.</font>

329
00:20:20,872 --> 00:20:24,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">These are the test sheets from last year.
I thought you could study from them.</font>

330
00:20:25,305 --> 00:20:27,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks. They'll be a big help.</font>

331
00:20:29,305 --> 00:20:31,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry that I'm dressed so sloppy.</font>

332
00:20:33,205 --> 00:20:35,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Do I look funny?</font>

333
00:20:35,205 --> 00:20:38,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No, I'm actually really happy.
-Huh?</font>

334
00:20:38,605 --> 00:20:42,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, the other day you also
let me see you in that jersey at work.</font>

335
00:20:42,772 --> 00:20:44,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, well that's--</font>

336
00:20:44,705 --> 00:20:48,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It seems like you're taking me
more seriously since I said I like you.</font>

337
00:20:50,205 --> 00:20:51,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not what's going on--</font>

338
00:20:51,705 --> 00:20:54,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing standing there
at my door?</font>

339
00:20:58,072 --> 00:21:00,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why don't you take this opportunity
to clear things up.</font>

340
00:21:00,905 --> 00:21:02,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

341
00:21:02,405 --> 00:21:04,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are your feelings?</font>

342
00:21:04,839 --> 00:21:05,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Daichi.</font>

343
00:21:06,972 --> 00:21:07,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you still--</font>

344
00:21:08,039 --> 00:21:09,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are your feelings about Yuri now?</font>

345
00:21:12,405 --> 00:21:14,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You liked her, didn't you?</font>

346
00:21:27,939 --> 00:21:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks to Nao,
it looks like you're eating properly.</font>

347
00:21:31,205 --> 00:21:33,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But also as a way
of saying thanks to you two,</font>

348
00:21:33,772 --> 00:21:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought I'd make dinner.</font>

349
00:21:36,705 --> 00:21:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisa will eat anything,</font>

350
00:21:38,205 --> 00:21:41,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but he's never liked stew
since he was little.</font>

351
00:21:41,305 --> 00:21:43,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I didn't either. I wonder why?</font>

352
00:21:43,205 --> 00:21:44,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe since it's
so clearly a family dish--</font>

353
00:21:44,972 --> 00:21:46,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come you haven't said anything?</font>

354
00:21:48,305 --> 00:21:49,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

355
00:21:53,705 --> 00:21:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Could it be... you always knew?</font>

356
00:22:01,772 --> 00:22:03,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You knew that I always liked Yuri?</font>

357
00:22:07,072 --> 00:22:08,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you even listening?</font>

358
00:22:11,905 --> 00:22:13,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look at me!</font>

359
00:22:16,472 --> 00:22:18,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not Yuri.</font>

360
00:22:19,472 --> 00:22:20,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

361
00:22:25,772 --> 00:22:27,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri is the one thing
I won't let you have.</font>

362
00:22:31,305 --> 00:22:32,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Takuya.</font>

363
00:22:34,705 --> 00:22:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, Hisa.</font>

364
00:22:47,205 --> 00:22:48,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait, Uehara!</font>

365
00:23:01,939 --> 00:23:03,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Damn you!</i></font>

366
00:23:07,305 --> 00:23:09,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri, when did you get here?</font>

367
00:23:09,472 --> 00:23:10,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Damn you!</font>

368
00:23:33,472 --> 00:23:34,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

369
00:23:37,405 --> 00:23:39,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For eight whole years...</font>

370
00:23:40,905 --> 00:23:43,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he acted like he didn't know.</font>

371
00:23:45,605 --> 00:23:47,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">God damn that jerk!</font>

372
00:23:54,805 --> 00:23:56,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I feel like such an idiot.</font>

373
00:23:58,605 --> 00:24:01,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This whole time
I was desperately hiding my feelings.</font>

374
00:24:07,572 --> 00:24:09,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He didn't let you have her.</font>

375
00:24:11,472 --> 00:24:12,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

376
00:24:13,805 --> 00:24:16,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He didn't give you a silly smile
and let you have her, right?</font>

377
00:24:21,972 --> 00:24:24,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was really admirable of Takuya.</font>

378
00:24:25,672 --> 00:24:28,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's the kind of big brother you deserve.</font>

379
00:24:36,505 --> 00:24:38,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

380
00:24:55,572 --> 00:24:57,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Get me closer.
-You're heavy, you know.</font>

381
00:24:57,772 --> 00:24:59,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But I can't see.
-What?</font>

382
00:24:59,839 --> 00:25:02,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Lift me a little higher.
-I can't go any higher. Ow!</font>

383
00:25:03,305 --> 00:25:06,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uh, it's not here.
-What?</font>

384
00:25:08,772 --> 00:25:09,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

385
00:25:11,072 --> 00:25:13,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-There it is!
-Really?</font>

386
00:25:16,872 --> 00:25:18,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here it is!</font>

387
00:25:18,405 --> 00:25:19,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh.</font>

388
00:25:19,605 --> 00:25:21,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, come on. Let me see.</font>

389
00:25:21,572 --> 00:25:24,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, what're you hiding it for? Show me!</font>

390
00:25:25,205 --> 00:25:27,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Fine!
-What's with you?</font>

391
00:25:29,805 --> 00:25:31,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just a key ring!</font>

392
00:25:39,572 --> 00:25:40,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao?</font>

393
00:25:42,939 --> 00:25:44,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

394
00:25:44,305 --> 00:25:47,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing out here?
It's freezing. You'll catch a cold.</font>

395
00:25:48,205 --> 00:25:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I've got to find a ring.
-A ring?</font>

396
00:25:52,705 --> 00:25:56,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri's marriage ring.
Uehara's looking for it.</font>

397
00:26:02,672 --> 00:26:06,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But that's got nothing to do with you,
Nao.</font>

398
00:26:06,472 --> 00:26:08,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You've got tests--
-It matters to me.</font>

399
00:26:10,005 --> 00:26:12,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's more important than tests.</font>

400
00:26:18,305 --> 00:26:19,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

401
00:26:59,305 --> 00:27:00,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You get back home.</font>

402
00:27:03,305 --> 00:27:04,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't do that.</font>

403
00:27:05,405 --> 00:27:07,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'll keep looking until--
-Go home.</font>

404
00:27:08,505 --> 00:27:09,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is...</font>

405
00:27:13,305 --> 00:27:14,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">my responsibility.</font>

406
00:27:19,805 --> 00:27:23,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides, unlike me, you're pretty dumb.</font>

407
00:27:23,505 --> 00:27:26,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't be having you hate me
because you failed your tests.</font>

408
00:27:27,005 --> 00:27:30,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What a joke it would be
if you were held back.</font>

409
00:27:30,805 --> 00:27:32,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My grades aren't that bad.</font>

410
00:27:33,205 --> 00:27:36,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides, if I take remedial lessons,
I won't be held back.</font>

411
00:27:36,405 --> 00:27:39,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Taking remedial lessons
is a problem itself.</font>

412
00:27:39,305 --> 00:27:42,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your problem is
that you never usually study anyway.</font>

413
00:27:43,305 --> 00:27:46,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Whose fault do you think it is
that I've gotten all wrapped up in this?</font>

414
00:27:46,205 --> 00:27:48,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like I said,
forget about this and go home!</font>

415
00:27:50,839 --> 00:27:54,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, fine! I <i>will go home!</i></font>

416
00:27:57,705 --> 00:27:59,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you sure you want me to?</font>

417
00:28:09,972 --> 00:28:11,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh dear!</font>

418
00:28:14,105 --> 00:28:15,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

419
00:28:15,872 --> 00:28:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez! What's wrong with you? You're heavy.</font>

420
00:28:18,405 --> 00:28:20,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow!</font>

421
00:28:21,105 --> 00:28:22,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I am not heavy!</font>

422
00:28:38,205 --> 00:28:39,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't believe this.</font>

423
00:29:11,705 --> 00:29:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

424
00:29:14,105 --> 00:29:16,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

425
00:29:18,072 --> 00:29:19,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here it is!</font>

426
00:29:20,005 --> 00:29:21,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here it is! Here it is!</font>

427
00:29:35,805 --> 00:29:38,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here it is! Here it is, Uehara!</font>

428
00:29:38,505 --> 00:29:39,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

429
00:29:40,005 --> 00:29:42,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here it is! Here it is! We did it, Uehara!</font>

430
00:29:43,305 --> 00:29:45,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's dangerous. Give it back to me.</font>

431
00:29:53,505 --> 00:29:54,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

432
00:29:57,072 --> 00:29:58,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

433
00:29:59,005 --> 00:30:00,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

434
00:30:01,872 --> 00:30:04,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Aw, jeez.</font>

435
00:30:04,205 --> 00:30:06,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I said, "Thank you."</font>

436
00:30:06,072 --> 00:30:07,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

437
00:30:09,105 --> 00:30:10,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Don't get carried away.</i></font>

438
00:30:15,472 --> 00:30:16,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow.</font>

439
00:30:16,705 --> 00:30:19,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, all right. Here, let me see.</font>

440
00:30:19,505 --> 00:30:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Pain, pain, go away!</font>

441
00:30:22,072 --> 00:30:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That made it worse.</font>

442
00:30:30,171 --> 00:30:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome back, Hisa.</font>

443
00:30:34,205 --> 00:30:35,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks.</font>

444
00:30:40,772 --> 00:30:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're back.</font>

445
00:30:42,672 --> 00:30:44,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey.</font>

446
00:30:44,605 --> 00:30:46,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What have you two been up to?</font>

447
00:30:46,905 --> 00:30:48,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri!</font>

448
00:30:48,205 --> 00:30:51,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait a sec. Have you two already made up?</font>

449
00:30:51,405 --> 00:30:52,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't talk like that.</font>

450
00:30:52,972 --> 00:30:55,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What I want to know is
where you guys have been.</font>

451
00:30:57,872 --> 00:30:58,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

452
00:31:03,505 --> 00:31:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't let her take it off again.</font>

453
00:31:07,305 --> 00:31:08,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisa!</font>

454
00:31:11,305 --> 00:31:12,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

455
00:31:19,472 --> 00:31:20,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

456
00:31:24,205 --> 00:31:25,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

457
00:31:26,772 --> 00:31:29,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks for scolding me,
and saying it would be cruel to Uehara.</font>

458
00:31:31,072 --> 00:31:32,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're absolutely right.</font>

459
00:31:32,905 --> 00:31:34,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri.</font>

460
00:31:34,105 --> 00:31:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

461
00:31:35,839 --> 00:31:38,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's none of your business.
-Why?</font>

462
00:31:39,605 --> 00:31:40,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Right?
-Right?</font>

463
00:31:40,605 --> 00:31:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's that all about?</font>

464
00:31:49,605 --> 00:31:52,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>This is my responsibility.</i></font>

465
00:32:06,305 --> 00:32:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello, Daichi?</font>

466
00:32:08,505 --> 00:32:10,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can I meet you somewhere today?</font>

467
00:32:12,005 --> 00:32:14,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have something important to tell you.</font>

468
00:32:22,105 --> 00:32:23,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here goes.</font>

469
00:32:24,505 --> 00:32:27,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">EVENING STAR RAMEN</font>

470
00:32:27,305 --> 00:32:29,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-Welcome!
-Sorry.</i></font>

471
00:32:29,505 --> 00:32:31,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I couldn't wait, and started without you.</i></font>

472
00:32:31,672 --> 00:32:33,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Closer to your house would have been fine.</font>

473
00:32:33,905 --> 00:32:36,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't mind. I like the ramen here.</font>

474
00:32:36,972 --> 00:32:40,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides, this place isn't dark or boring.</font>

475
00:32:40,839 --> 00:32:41,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here you go.</font>

476
00:32:42,305 --> 00:32:43,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Issei.</font>

477
00:32:48,305 --> 00:32:49,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

478
00:32:52,105 --> 00:32:55,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've come to apologize to you today.</font>

479
00:32:59,705 --> 00:33:01,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

480
00:33:04,105 --> 00:33:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao?</font>

481
00:33:05,505 --> 00:33:06,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

482
00:33:07,672 --> 00:33:11,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've taken advantage of your kindness
to me.</font>

483
00:33:11,605 --> 00:33:13,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I always have.</font>

484
00:33:14,305 --> 00:33:16,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Don't worry about that.
-I'm sorry.</font>

485
00:33:16,205 --> 00:33:18,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like I said, don't apologize.</font>

486
00:33:20,105 --> 00:33:23,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You haven't done anything
to apologize for, anyway.</font>

487
00:33:26,705 --> 00:33:28,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

488
00:33:29,105 --> 00:33:30,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is really good!</font>

489
00:33:31,972 --> 00:33:34,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The ramen here really is great, isn't it?</font>

490
00:33:39,205 --> 00:33:40,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is great.</font>

491
00:33:49,572 --> 00:33:51,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's cold.
-It's cold.</font>

492
00:33:54,572 --> 00:33:55,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here.</font>

493
00:33:57,872 --> 00:33:59,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm fine.</font>

494
00:33:59,872 --> 00:34:01,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, OK.</font>

495
00:34:02,305 --> 00:34:04,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, I'll see you later.</font>

496
00:34:05,772 --> 00:34:06,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

497
00:34:07,105 --> 00:34:09,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't make that face.</font>

498
00:34:12,205 --> 00:34:15,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm glad that thing
with Yuri has been cleared up now.</font>

499
00:34:19,005 --> 00:34:20,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you.</font>

500
00:34:40,405 --> 00:34:42,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The ring...</font>

501
00:34:54,805 --> 00:34:56,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm home.</font>

502
00:34:57,105 --> 00:34:59,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, how's it going?</font>

503
00:35:04,505 --> 00:35:07,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Did you eat already?</font>

504
00:35:08,505 --> 00:35:11,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. I'm full.</font>

505
00:35:11,839 --> 00:35:14,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see.</font>

506
00:35:24,105 --> 00:35:28,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's all quiet now
without Yuri and Takuya.</font>

507
00:35:29,105 --> 00:35:32,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. So, you want to watch some TV?</font>

508
00:35:39,472 --> 00:35:41,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you want for lunch?</font>

509
00:35:41,405 --> 00:35:43,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? I thought you already ate.</font>

510
00:35:43,839 --> 00:35:45,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah.</font>

511
00:35:45,705 --> 00:35:49,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I was just thinking how I'd like
some of the stew Takuya made.</font>

512
00:35:49,805 --> 00:35:51,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-OK?
-Yeah.</font>

513
00:35:54,205 --> 00:35:56,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I'll have to heat it up.</font>

514
00:36:14,672 --> 00:36:15,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">By the way...</font>

515
00:36:16,205 --> 00:36:17,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

516
00:36:19,572 --> 00:36:23,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yesterday... Well, I mean...</font>

517
00:36:23,605 --> 00:36:25,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This thing that's happened...</font>

518
00:36:26,105 --> 00:36:29,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I mean, this whole time lately</font>

519
00:36:30,672 --> 00:36:31,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry I got you involved.</font>

520
00:36:35,205 --> 00:36:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't mind.</font>

521
00:36:39,405 --> 00:36:44,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks to you... I've been able to
get over a lot of things.</font>

522
00:36:48,105 --> 00:36:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean...</font>

523
00:36:51,305 --> 00:36:53,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This time it's for real.</font>

524
00:37:00,605 --> 00:37:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Me too.</font>

525
00:37:06,572 --> 00:37:11,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because of this, I guess you could say
I've learned a lot about myself.</font>

526
00:37:14,805 --> 00:37:15,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh.</font>

527
00:37:17,705 --> 00:37:19,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

528
